quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  22,1,logo! apne perwar-digaar se daro. ke qayamat ka zalzala aik hadisaaٴ azeem hoga
  22,2,( ae mukhatib ) jis din to is ko dekhe ga ( uss din yeh haal hoga ke ) tamam doodh pilanay wali aurtain apne bachon ko bhool jayen gi. aur tamam hamal valyon ke hamal gir parrin ge. aur log tujh ko matawaale nazar ayen ge magar woh matawaale nahi hon ge balkay ( azaab dekh kar ) madhosh ho rahay hon ge. be shak khuda ka azaab bara sakht hai
  22,3,aur baaz log aisay hain jo khuda ( ki shaan ) mein ilm ( o dansih ) ke baghair jhagarte aur har shetan sarkash ki pairwi karte hain
  22,4,jis ke baray mein likh diya gaya hai ke jo usay dost rakhay ga to is ko gumraah kardey ga aur dozakh ke azaab ka rasta dukhaay ga
  22,5,logo agar tum ko marnay ke baad jee utney mein kuch shak ho to hum ne tum ko ( pehli baar bhi to ) pedakiya tha ( yani ibtida mein ) matti se phir is se nutfa bana kar. phir is se khoon ka lothrha bana kar. phir is se booti bana kar jis ki banawat kaamil bhi hoti hai aur naaqis bhi taakay tum par ( apni khaalqiyat ) zahir kar dein. aur hum jis ko chahtay hain aik meyaad muqarrar taq pait mein thehraye rakhtay hain phir tum ko bacha bana kar nikaltay hain. phir tum jawani ko pahunchte ho. aur baaz ( qabal az peeri mrjate hain aur baaz Sheikh fali ho jatay aur burhapay ki ) nihayat kharab Umar ki taraf lout’tay jatay hain ke bohat kuch jan-nay ke baad bilkul be ilm ho jatay hain. aur ( ae dekhnay walay ) to daikhta hai ( ke aik waqt mein ) zameen khushk ( pari hoti hai ) phir jab hum is par meen barastee hain to shadaab hojati aur ubharnay lagti hai aur terhan terhan ki baronq cheezein ugati hai
